# **Part 2**

## **Describe a successful business person you admire.**

One successful business person I really admire is Jensen Huang, who is the founder and CEO of NVIDIA. I first learned about him a few years ago when I became interested in artificial intelligence and computer hardware. Since then, I’ve followed many of his interviews and speeches, and I’ve been deeply impressed by both his vision and leadership style.

NVIDIA originally focused on graphics cards for gaming, but under his leadership, the company gradually became one of the most important technology companies in the world, especially in the field of AI. Nowadays, NVIDIA’s GPUs are widely used in machine learning, robotics, autonomous driving, and scientific research. In a way, many recent breakthroughs in AI wouldn’t have developed so quickly without the computing power provided by NVIDIA.

I think he is successful for several reasons. First of all, he has extremely strong long-term vision. Years before AI became globally popular, he already believed that GPUs would become essential for artificial intelligence and high-performance computing. Secondly, he seems very resilient and hardworking. I once watched an interview where he mentioned that running a company is full of pressure and uncertainty, but he still remained determined and optimistic.

What I admire most about him is that he’s not only a businessman focused on profits, but also someone who genuinely pushes technology forward. He often talks about innovation, the future of AI, and how technology can improve society. As someone who studies computer science and hopes to work in AI in the future, I find him extremely inspiring. He makes me feel that technology is not just about making money, but also about creating meaningful change in the world.

---

## **中文翻译：**

我非常欣赏的一位成功商人是英伟达的创始人兼CEO黄仁勋。我几年前开始对人工智能和计算机硬件感兴趣时认识了他。从那以后，我看了很多他的采访和演讲，对他的远见和领导力印象非常深刻。

英伟达最开始主要做游戏显卡，但在他的带领下，公司逐渐成为全球最重要的科技公司之一，尤其是在人工智能领域。现在英伟达的GPU被广泛用于机器学习、机器人、自动驾驶和科学研究。从某种程度上说，近几年很多AI突破如果没有英伟达提供的算力，发展不会这么快。

我认为他成功有几个原因。首先，他有非常强的长期眼光。在AI还没有全球爆发之前，他就已经意识到GPU对人工智能的重要性。其次，他非常坚韧、勤奋。我曾经看过一个采访，他提到经营公司充满压力和不确定性，但他依然保持坚定和乐观。

我最欣赏他的一点是，他不仅仅是一个追求利润的商人，更是真正推动科技发展的人。他经常谈创新、AI未来以及科技如何改善社会。作为一个学习计算机科学并希望未来从事AI的人，我觉得他非常鼓舞人心。他让我意识到，科技不仅仅是赚钱，更是改变世界。

